Class DefaultBoxJSONResponseParser

java.lang.Object

Direct Known Subclasses:

public class DefaultBoxJSONResponseParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBoxResponseParser

This class is a wrapper class in order for Jackson JSON processor to parse response JSON into the wrapped objects.

Constructor Detail

DefaultBoxJSONResponseParser

public DefaultBoxJSONResponseParser(java.lang.Class objectClass,
                                    ObjectMapper objectMapper)
Constructor.

Parameters:
objectClass - class of the wrapped object. Response from API will be parsed into this object, caller needs to make sure this class has fields with same names as the JSON part of API response. If class contains more fields than the JSON, those fields will be left null. If the class contains less fields than the JSON, the parsing will error out.
objectMapper - ObjectMapper to be used when parsing.
